---
import PageLayout from "@layouts/PageLayout.astro"
import TopLayout from "@layouts/TopLayout.astro"
import BottomLayout from "@layouts/BottomLayout.astro"
import { MY_STORY } from "@consts"
---

<PageLayout title={MY_STORY.TITLE} description={MY_STORY.DESCRIPTION}>
  <TopLayout>
    <div class="animate page-heading">
      {MY_STORY.TITLE}
    </div>
  </TopLayout>

  <BottomLayout>
      <!-- About Section -->
      <section class="animate">
        <article>
          <p>I am a <b><i>software engineer</i></b>, <b><i>laravel artisan</i></b>, <b><i>neovim user</i></b>, <b><i>dev tools / packages enthusiast</i></b>, <b><i>open source contributor</i></b> and <b><i>all around nice guy</i></b>.</p>

          <h4>During my career</h4>
          <p>Professionally I work mainly in web SAAS agile development using Laravel and Vue.js in a fast, demanding and changing environment where speed, planning and iterating are key factors.</p>

          <h4>What I like to code on my own</h4>
          <p>I like building cool dev tools, packages and ideas I also like contributing and discovering open source tools and projects.</p>

          <h4><i>- âˆž</i></h4>
          <p>I used to hate computers, I didn't even own a proper one. I always was a console type of guy.</p>

          <h4><i>2017</i></h4>
          <p>I've done great in my studies until I made it to university studying a mix of science and technology. <b><i>I felt lost.</i></b></p>

          <h4><i>2020</i></h4>
          <p>I dropout of university to search my true passion.</p>

          <h4><i>2021</i></h4>
          <p>my passion turned out to be <b><i>coding.</i></b> I went for an associate degree in web and mobile development where we studied different technologies and principles.</p>

          <h4><i>2023</i></h4>
          <p>I fell in love with <b><i>laravel</i></b> and building, <b><i>the sky is the limit.</i></b> I landed my first internship during a beachless summer and I got hired after that summer, as a full-time full-stack developer.</p>
          <p><b><i>and that's the arc, from no world to hello world to let's build the world...</i></b></p>
        </article>
      </section>

  </BottomLayout>
</PageLayout>
